\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The characteristic of a field is the least positive integer
\begin_inset space ~
\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $m$
\end_inset

 such that 
\begin_inset Formula $m=1+1+1+\cdots+1=0$
\end_inset

, and if no such 
\begin_inset Formula $m$
\end_inset

